CSS:

the elements default display is block, default position is static.

1em = 16px = 100%;

Font-size: 90px = (90/16)*100 = 562.5%；（%的设置更灵活）

em 和 % 会inherited，如果父级设置了一个font-size : 2em，子级设置了一个font-size : 5em，则最后这个子级的展现是：2em + 5em = 7em. （“em”和“%”使用要慎重）。

But！使用“rem”可以避免子级延用了父级的“em”内容。（most recommend!!!）


CSS specificity——

1)The universal selectors have the lowest rank;
2)The class selectors have the middle rank;
3)The ID selectors have the highest rank;


HTML hierarchy——
Inline style > internal style > external style;


Combine these two rules above——
Inline style > ID selectors


!important:
Very useful when you are making a bootstrap carousel button !!!
eg/: when you want to make the indicator button (default style is stripe) to a circle-shape:
   
The “!important” reference will make it override the default bootstrap button style!

#ID .class { }：可以用于specific指明这个ID里面这个class；

.parent-class .child-class {} 是可以制定某个特定class的；

指向CSS时，有空格：前半句是parent(class or ID)，空格后面接child的elements/class；
无空格：则单指特定的element；


eg/: 无空格

1)h1.class：means a h1 element has a class named “class”;
2)h1#id：means a h1 element has an ID named “id”;
3)h1#id.class：means a h1 element has an ID named “id”, and a class named “class”;



CSS空格符：“&nbsp;” 

Unordered-list (ul) 如果不要bullets：{ list-style-type: none; }

图片如果要自适应屏幕大小：{background-size: cover;}

取消"autofucus"时input聚焦的边框：outline:none；

css如何让div在顶部固定不动？
{ position: fixed;
  top: 0;}


Viewport Height: (vh)
Viewport Height (vh). This unit is based on the height of the viewport. A value of 1vh is equal to 1% of the viewport height.
